            <p><b>Description:</b> As a new user, I want to register for an account using my email address and a secure password so I can access the app's full features.</p>

<p><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b></p>

<ul>
	<li>User can access a registration form.</li>
	<li>User can enter a valid email address (e.g., <span class="error">&#91;email address removed&#93;</span>).</li>
	<li>User can create a password meeting minimum complexity requirements (e.g., 8 characters, combination of uppercase/lowercase letters, numbers, and symbols).</li>
	<li>User can confirm the password by re-entering it.</li>
	<li>User can optionally provide additional information like name (optional).</li>
	<li>Upon submitting the form, the system validates the entered information.</li>
	<li>If validation is successful, a confirmation email is sent to the provided email address.</li>
	<li>The confirmation email contains a link to verify the account.</li>
	<li>Clicking the verification link in the email activates the user account.</li>
	<li>After successful account activation, the user is redirected to a login page or a welcome message.</li>
</ul>

